Package: phynotype
Title: Clustering and Consensus Meta-Clustering
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: person("Imad", "El Badisy", email = "elbadisyimad@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Imad El Badisy [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Imad El Badisy <elbadisyimad@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for clustering, consensus meta-clustering,
    validation, exploratory interpretation, cluster prediction, and standardized
    plotting. The package provides a clustering workflow with consensus clustering following Strehl and Ghosh (2002)
    <https://www.jmlr.org/papers/v3/strehl02a.html>.
URL: https://github.com/ielbadisy/phynotype, https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=phynotype
BugReports: https://github.com/ielbadisy/phynotype/issues
